author: commercialappeal.com
title: How the Dandy Dozen fared in Week 9
text:
1. Whitehaven (7-1) was idle
Next: Friday at Collierville
2. East (7-1) beat Millington, 56-12, Thursday
Next: Thursday vs. MLK Prep at Raleigh-Egypt
3. MUS (6-2) beat Briarcrest, 31-12
Next: Friday vs. Craigmont
4. Munford (8-0) beat Overton, 42-8, Thursday
Next: Friday at Brighton
5. CBHS (6-2) beat St. Benedict, 49-13
Next: Friday vs. Catholic
6. White Station (5-3) was idle
Next: Friday vs. Germantown at the Fairgrounds
7. Cordova (7-1) was idle
Next: Friday vs. Houston
8. Southwind (6-2) lost to Central, 30-28
Next: Friday at Bolton
9. Northpoint (9-0) beat Harding, 12-7
Next: Friday vs. Fayette-Ware
10. St. George's (7-1) beat Tipton-Rosemark, 73-7
Next: Friday vs. Fayette-Ware
11. Olive Branch (5-3) beat Horn Lake, 38-28
Next: Friday at Columbus
12. DeSoto Central (6-3) beat Hernando, 39-16
Next: Friday at Tupelo
